sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3<br/>(openshift-ingress)
    participant HTTPRoute as HTTPRoute<br/>(Gateway API)
    participant MLflowSvc as MLflow Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant MLflowPod as MLflow Server Pod<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3<br/>kubernetes-auth
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: User Access to MLflow via Gateway

    User->>Gateway: GET/POST /mlflow/*<br/>Bearer Token (K8s)
    Gateway->>HTTPRoute: Route lookup<br/>/mlflow path prefix
    HTTPRoute->>MLflowSvc: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    MLflowSvc->>MLflowPod: Forward to Pod<br/>Bearer Token (forwarded)
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: self_subject_access_review<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>Validate user Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Authorization result
    MLflowPod-->>User: MLflow UI/API Response<br/>JSON/HTML

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: MLflow Operator Reconciliation

    participant OpPod as Operator Pod
    participant Helm as Embedded Helm Chart

    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Watch MLflow CRs<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: MLflow CR created/updated
    OpPod->>Helm: Render templates<br/>Local filesystem
    Helm-->>OpPod: Kubernetes manifests
    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>Deployment, Service, HTTPRoute, etc.<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: Resources created

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 3: MLflow Artifact Storage (Remote S3)

    User->>MLflowPod: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/create<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: Validate Bearer Token<br/>self_subject_access_review
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Authorized
    MLflowPod->>PostgreSQL: Store experiment metadata<br/>Username/Password<br/>TLS 1.2+
    PostgreSQL-->>MLflowPod: Metadata saved
    User->>MLflowPod: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-artifact<br/>Bearer Token + Artifact data
    MLflowPod->>S3: PUT s3://bucket/path/artifact<br/>AWS IAM/Access Keys<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>MLflowPod: Artifact stored
    MLflowPod-->>User: Success response

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Prom->>OpPod: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    OpPod-->>Prom: Operator metrics<br/>Prometheus format
